bgraphs. Labels \u22645 words.\n\n---\n**NEXT STEP:** Adapt the template above to the user's request. Call `run_python` with the complete script. Remember: `gs_theme`, `save_artifact`, `PRIMARY`, `CAT_PALETTE`, `_db`, and all constants are pre-imported \u2014 no imports needed. Use `:Q` for numbers, `:T` for dates, `:N` for categories. Do NOT call `.interactive()`.",
